 Where Health Meets Happiness Unleash your dog's energy! Get Started Introduction Canine Cardio Hawaii LLC is Hawaii's first and only veterinary professional owned mobile dog gym! We are a Kailua based, female owned and operated, dog-powered exercise service that provides an easy and safe alternative way to exercise your dog. I come to your home and provide a fulfilling and safe workout for your dog in my fully equipped and climate controlled trailer. I am here to help the dogs of Hawai'i live a happier, healthier, and longer life through regular exercise. Canine Cardio Hawaii is where health meets happiness! What is a mobile dog gym? 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 Temperature Controlled Our trailer is equipped with cold air conditioning to ensure that your dog can exercise comfortably, no matter the weather conditions outside. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 100% Pup-Powered Our treadmills (called slatmills) are specifically designed with dogs in mind. They are low resistance, low impact, and have no motor, so your dog can go as fast (or slow) as they want and even stop if they are tired. Safety is ensured by clipping the dogs harness to the slatmill so that they don't fall off and dogs are continuously monitored by our expert coach.
